    {
      "Text": "Security update for systemd",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for systemd fixes the following issue\n\nSecurity issues fixed:\n  \n- CVE-2026-40226: nspawn: escape-to-host via malformed optional config file (bsc#1261400).\n\nOther updates and bugfixes:\n\n- Import commit 37508f8ec1 (bsc#1267647).\n- Import commit c7530fbea3 (bsc#1261982 bsc#1261983).\n- Import commit 5c4ed461a7 (bsc#1261982).\n- Import commit 4b963df038 (bsc#1261983).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
